    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "HTML Table - Colspan"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To make a cell span over multiple columns, use the colspan attribute:"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "html",
          "code": "<table>  <tr>    <th colspan=\"2\">Name</th>    \n  <th>Age</th>  </tr>  <tr>    \n  <td>Jill</td>    <td>Smith</td>    \n  <td>43</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td>Eve</td>    \n  <td>Jackson</td>    <td>57</td>  </tr></table>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "other",
      "text": "Note: The value of the colspan attribute represents the number of columns to span."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "HTML Table - Rowspan"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To make a cell span over multiple rows, use the rowspan attribute:"
    },
    {
      "type": "example",
      "description": "",
      "codes": [
        {
          "language": "html",
          "code": "<table>  <tr>    <th>Name</th>    \n  <td>Jill</td>  </tr>  <tr>    <th rowspan=\"2\">Phone</th>    \n  <td>555-1234</td>  </tr>  <tr>    \n  <td>555-8745</td></tr></table>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "other",
      "text": "Note: The value of the rowspan attribute represents the number of \nrows to span."
    },
